title: I Don't Think I'm Ready For This (Holly Furtick)
description: God has prepared you (even when you don't feel ready). In “I Don't Think I'm Ready For This,” the first lady of Elevation Church, Holly Furtick, teaches that even when we don't feel ready for the next step, God has already made a way ahead of us.
